resource/Emmanuel_Macron\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Emmanuel_Macron\"}, {\"begin\": 871, \"end\": 877, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"score\": 0.9901749125143525, \"rank\": 0.007802980033006402, \"text\": \"French\", \"types\": [\"Q315\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\"}, {\"begin\": 906, \"end\": 913, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China\", \"score\": 0.915196146186184, \"rank\": 0.09265823800722196, \"text\": \"Chinese\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"President Macron and his wife asked Shen to convey their sincere greetings to President Xi and his wife, congratulated the Chinese athletes for their outstanding performances, and thanked the Chinese government for its support of France in hosting the Olympic Games.\", \"from\": 935, \"to\": 1201, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 935, \"end\": 951, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Emmanuel_Macron\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"President Macron\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Emmanuel_Macron\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Emmanuel_Macron\"}, {\"begin\": 1058, \"end\": 1065, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China\", \"score\": 0.915196146186184, \"rank\": 0.09265823800722196, \"text\": \"Chinese\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China\"}, {\"begin\": 1127, \"end\": 1145, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Government_of_China\", \"score\": 0.999999879547211, \"rank\": 8.579254766395996e-08, \"text\": \"Chinese government\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Government_of_China\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Government_of_China\"}, {\"begin\": 1165, \"end\": 1171, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"score\": 0.9708291901429708, \"rank\": 0.02942520213994774, \"text\": \"France\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"During her meeting with International Olympic Committee\\u00a0(IOC) President Thomas Bach on Saturday, Shen said China is willing to deepen its high-level friendly cooperation with the IOC, and stands ready to work with the IOC to make new and greater contributions to promoting the development of the Olympic Movement and building a community with a shared future for mankind.\", \"from\": 1203, \"to\": 1574, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1227, \"end\": 1258, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"International Olympic Committee\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\"}, {\"begin\": 1260, \"end\": 1263, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.5579877567802413e-15, \"text\": \"IOC\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\"}, {\"begin\": 1275, \"end\": 1286, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Thomas_Bach\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Thomas Bach\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Thomas_Bach\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Thomas_Bach\"}, {\"begin\": 1310, \"end\": 1315, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China\", \"score\": 0.9999640343220496, \"rank\": 3.5042372938521476e-05, \"text\"